VA loans finance properties with multiple units?"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "What Happens If You Didn't Live in the Property as Required?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Failing to meet VA occupancy requirements represents a serious issue with potential consequences:"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "How Do VA Loans Work for Native American Veterans?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "What special provisions exist for Native American veterans?"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Can You Get a VA Loan After Bankruptcy or Foreclosure?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "How do past credit issues affect VA loan eligibility?"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "What Documentation Do You Need for VA Loans?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "What paperwork is required for VA loan applications?"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "How Do VA Loans Handle Gift Funds?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Can family members contribute funds toward VA loan purchases?"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Can VA Loans Finance Condominiums?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "What condominium requirements apply to VA financing?"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "How Do VA Loans Handle Manufactured Homes?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Can you use VA benefits for manufactured housing?"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "What Are VA Loan Limits?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Do VA loans cap financing amounts?"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Can You Refinance a VA Loan Into a Conventional Loan?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. Veterans can refinance VA loans into conventional financing when this strategy makes sense. Reasons to consider this include:"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "How Does Divorce Affect VA Loans?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "What happens to VA loans during divorce proceedings?"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "What Properties Don't Qualify for VA Financing?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "What types of properties can't use VA loans?"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "How Do You Restore VA Loan Entitlement?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "What steps restore VA benefits after previous use?"}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Can National Guard and Reserve Members Use VA Loans?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "What requirements apply to Guard and Reserve members?"}}]};
